To install, do the following:

sudo apt-get install perl-tk libgtk2-imageview-perl libdevice-serialport-perl \
libfile-homedir-perl libfile-slurp-perl
sudo cpanp i Tk::Help
sudo cpanp i Ham::Locator

Allow your user ID to access the serial port
sudo usermod -a -G dialout $USER

Download rotator-control to a directory of your choosing and run
`chmod 555 rotator-control` to make it executable.

